<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Quotes Ready – My Car Quote</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #333;
    }
    .box {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: auto;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 30px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    .logo {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .logo img {
      max-width: 160px;
      height: auto;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 10px;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      background: #28a745;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
      white-space: nowrap;
      max-width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    .small {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .btn {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
        font-size: 16px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="box">
    <div class="logo">
      <img src="cid:logoemailcid" alt="My Car Quote Logo" width="160" style="display:block; margin:auto;" />
    </div>

    <h2>Hello<%= customerName ? ` ${customerName}` : '' %>,</h2>

    <p>Your job request <strong>#<%= job.id %></strong> has received multiple quotes from  bodyshops.</p>

    <p>You can now review all your quotes and choose  — pay securely to reveal full details.</p>

    <a class="btn" href="<%= paymentUrl || (baseUrl + '/payment?jobId=' + job.id) %>">View Quotes & Pay</a>

    <p class="small">Thanks for using My Car Quote — helping you compare and choose with confidence.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
